{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894109961,"sessionID":"ses_2847705e7ffepD8FdURGtoeu3g","part":{"id":"prt_d7b89990a001aNx2jOOTGdwClg","messageID":"msg_d7b8989bb001L40TLzTXuGz5Nb","sessionID":"ses_2847705e7ffepD8FdURGtoeu3g","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_97043ec8cb6f40fbb5a25468","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Design: AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This document describes the technical implementation of a Docusaurus v3-based documentation site for the AgentCube project. The documentation framework provides a unified, maintainable, and extensible platform for technical documentation with support for versioning, internationalization (i18n), search, and automated deployment.\n6: \n7: ## Architecture\n8: \n9: ### Component Structure\n10: \n11: ```\n12: docs/\n13: ├── .gitignore                        # Git ignore for build artifacts\n14: ├── README.md                         # Documentation for working with docs\n15: ├── package.json                      # NPM dependencies and scripts\n16: ├── tsconfig.json                     # TypeScript configuration\n17: ├── docusaurus.config.ts              # Docusaurus site configuration\n18: ├── sidebars.ts                       # Documentation sidebar configuration\n19: ├── docs/                             # Markdown documentation files\n20: │   ├── intro/                        # Introduction documents\n21: │   ├── concepts/                     # Core concepts\n22: │   ├── crd-reference/                # CRD API reference\n23: │   ├── api-reference/                # REST API reference\n24: │   ├── sdk-cli/                      # SDK and CLI usage\n25: │   ├── deployment/                   # Deployment guides\n26: │   ├── configuration/                # Configuration reference\n27: │   ├── observability/                # Monitoring and logging\n28: │   ├── troubleshooting/              # FAQ and troubleshooting\n29: │   ├── requirements/                 # Architecture requirements (AR-001 ~ AR-042)\n30: │   └── contributing/                 # Contribution guidelines\n31: ├── src/                              # Custom React components\n32: │   ├── components/                   # Reusable components\n33: │   │   ├── CRDTable/                 # CRD field table component\n34: │   │   └── ArchitectureDiagram/      # Architecture diagram component\n35: │   ├── css/                          # Custom CSS styles\n36: │   │   └── custom.css\n37: │   └── pages/                        # Custom pages\n38: │       └── index.tsx                 # Home page\n39: ├── static/                           # Static assets\n40: │   ├── img/                          # Images and logos\n41: │   │   └── logo.svg\n42: │   ├── favicon.ico\n43: │   └── robots.txt\n44: └── i18n/                             # Internationalization (future)\n45:     ├── zh/                           # Chinese (default)\n46:     └── en/                           # English (future)\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### Integration Points\n50: \n51: - **GitHub Pages**: Automated deployment via GitHub Actions\n52: - **Algolia DocSearch**: Full-text search integration (optional)\n53: - **GitHub Discussions**: Community links in navigation\n54: - **Volcano Project**: Reference documentation and branding alignment\n55: \n56: ## Data Structures\n57: \n58: ### Docusaurus Config (`docusaurus.config.ts`)\n59: \n60: ```typescript\n61: interface Config {\n62:   title: string;                      // Site title: \"AgentCube\"\n63:   tagline: string;                    // Site description\n64:   favicon: string;                    // Path to favicon\n65:   url: string;                        // Production URL\n66:   baseUrl: string;                    // Base path: \"/agentcube/\"\n67:   organizationName: string;           // GitHub org: \"volcano-sh\"\n68:   projectName: string;                // GitHub repo: \"agentcube\"\n69:   onBrokenLinks: 'throw' | 'warn';    // Link validation behavior\n70:   onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'throw' | 'warn';\n71:   \n72:   i18n: {\n73:     defaultLocale: string;            // \"zh\"\n74:     locales: string[];                // [\"zh\", \"en\"]\n75:     localeConfigs: Record<string, {\n76:       htmlLang: string;\n77:       label: string;\n78:     }>;\n79:   };\n80:   \n81:   presets: [\n82:     '@docusaurus/preset-classic',\n83:     {\n84:       docs: DocsOptions;\n85:       blog: false;\n86:       theme: ThemeOptions;\n87:     }\n88:   ];\n89:   \n90:   themeConfig: {\n91:     navbar: NavbarConfig;\n92:     footer: FooterConfig;\n93:     prism: PrismConfig;\n94:     algolia?: AlgoliaConfig;\n95:   };\n96: }\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ### Package Dependencies (`package.json`)\n100: \n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 846. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n## Overview\n\nThis document describes the technical implementation of a Docusaurus v3-based documentation site for the AgentCube project. The documentation framework provides a unified, maintainable, and extensible platform for technical documentation with support for versioning, internationalization (i18n), search, and automated deployment.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Structure\n\n```\ndocs/\n├── .gitignore                        # Git ignore for build artifacts\n├── README.md                         # Documentation for working with docs\n├── package.json                      # NPM dependencies and scripts\n├── tsconfig.json                     # TypeScript configuration\n├── docusaurus.config.ts              # Docusaurus site configuration\n├── sidebars.ts                       # Documentation sidebar configuration\n├── docs/                             # Markdown documentation files\n│   ├── intro/                        # Introduction documents","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-042/design.md","time":{"start":1775894109930,"end":1775894109958}}}}
